FRONTLINE ROADS v0.32.10 FINAL AUDIT

Scope
- Recover full-screen menu/civilization/base/deployment panels after radar-quality changes on Android Chromium
- Isolate radar quality from interactive DOM panel composition
- Add backdrop/Escape emergency dismissal for all modal command panels

Root cause
- Touch devices defaulted to minimal, but the next quality value was full
- Full quality enabled modal backdrop blur
- Legacy comma-joined CSS selectors coupled radar quality to modal card and panel filter/clip rules
- The dark overlay remained interactive while the modal card could disappear from the compositor

Corrections
- Quality order: minimal -> balanced -> full
- Modal overlay backdrop filters: none
- Modal card opacity/visibility/filter: explicitly safe
- Quality-scoped modal selectors: removed
- Malformed selector/media-query coupling: removed
- Shared modal backdrop/Escape dismissal: menu, civilization, base command, deployment
- hidden and aria-hidden: synchronized

