- Save schema: 2 (unchanged)
- Existing radar preference storage key retained
- Existing saved full-quality setting remains valid and no longer hides command panels
- Combat, road acquisition, offline progression, deployment missions and construction ranges unchanged

Environment limitation
- Chromium in this execution environment blocks local/file navigation by administrator policy.
- Android GPU composition, touch interaction and Service Worker replacement require public HTTPS/device verification.
